('Diesel','https://www.thecocktaildb.com/images/media/drink/sxrrqq1454512852.jpg','232,98,63','1/2 pint,1/2 pint,1 dash','Pour the lager first then add the blackcurrant cordial. Top up with the cider. The colour sholud be very dark approaching the colour of Guiness.'),
