('Caipirissima','https://www.thecocktaildb.com/images/media/drink/yd47111503565515.jpg','250,381,416,216','2,2 tblsp,2-3 oz,crushed','Same as Caipirinha but instead of cachaca you add WHITE RUM. It''s great!!!!!!!!'),
