('Black & Tan','https://www.thecocktaildb.com/images/media/drink/rwpswp1454511017.jpg','14,210','1 part Bass pale,1 part','Fill pint glass half full with Bass. Next pour Guiness over a spoon slowly until glass is full. If done correctly the Guiness will stay on top and the Bass on bottom hence the name Black & Tan.'),
('Chocolate Milk','https://www.thecocktaildb.com/images/media/drink/j6q35t1504889399.jpg','99,270,15','1/2 shot,1/2 shot,1 dash','Put the milk in the bottom, pour the Liquer on top and add the dash of amaretto. Do not mix. SLAM IT!'),
('B-53','https://www.thecocktaildb.com/images/media/drink/rwqxrv1461866023.jpg','224,350,185','1/3 shot,1/3 shot,1/3 shot','Layer the Kahlua, Sambucca and Grand Marnier into a shot glas in that order. Better than B-52'),
