('Brainteaser','https://www.thecocktaildb.com/images/media/drink/ruywtq1461866066.jpg','350,160,8','30 ml white,30 ml,5 ml','layered erin first, then sambuca and then avocart(should sit in middle of other two. To drink: use a straw to suck up avocart then shot the rest and then suck fumes up through straw.'),
('Atlantic Sun','https://www.thecocktaildb.com/images/media/drink/doyxqb1493067556.jpg','1,364,296,384,106','2 cl Smirnoff,2 cl,2 cl,6 cl,1 dash','Shake all the ingredients, top the drink with soda. Garnish with a slice of orange.'),
